77 inline moveit_msgs::Constraints CartesianPathConstraintsBuilder::toPathConstraints() const
78 {
79  moveit_msgs::PositionConstraint pos_constraint;
80  pos_constraint.link_name = configuration_.getLinkName();
81  pos_constraint.constraint_region.primitive_poses.push_back(configuration_.getPose());
82 
83  moveit_msgs::Constraints path_constraints;
84  path_constraints.name = constraint_name_;
85  path_constraints.position_constraints.push_back(pos_constraint);
86  return path_constraints;
87 }
